verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Like a river glorious, is God’s perfect peace,
Over all victorious in its bright increase;
Perfect, yet it floweth fuller every day,
Perfect, yet it groweth deeper all the way.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Hidden in the hollow of God’s blessed hand,
Never foe can follow, never traitor stand;
Not a surge of worry, not a shade of care,
Not a blast of hurry touch the spirit there.{/lang-eng}
